                             'Thumper' 1.01

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Thumper' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} inspired by the 'sokoban'-type
games; you have to move various shapes with coloured patterns up to
their corresponding 'receiving' shapes. To move a shape, you have to
click on an empty space, or any empty receiving shape, located next
to it in order to 'thump' (or push) on that shape.

  Complete all the 25 game levels in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

